data.description: REDUCED - $295,000 3bdrm/2.5bath with office space. Roof has been replaced, updated LVP floors on main & bathrooms. Eat-in kitchen overlooks LR, replaced kitchen cabinets & sink, SS appliances, & granite counters. Separate laundry room w/cabinets.  Updated carpet, H2O heater, light fixtures & ceiling fans. Primary bathroom has been updated, new vanities, updated showers & LED mirror w/defogger, large linen closet, hall bath also updated. Deck backs up to wooded area for privacy. Roof was replaced in 2020. 2 car garage. Covered front porch, perfect for rocking chairs.
